txt.en: Your mission is to travel to Tûkurdul and recover supplies that got ransacked and save the driver if you can. Of course you should slay any kergrim you see in the area for good measure.
You found the ransacked shipment, the driver has already been slain.
You found the ransacked supplies, but you were too late to save the driver
Kergrim to the far north-west in Tûkurdul near Ashâgir ransacked a shipment from the west. They took the driver and the contents of his haul with them. Save the driver and recover his supplies.
'Hello, friend! I am glad you were able to recover the supplies, though it is sad to hear about the driver. Let us return to Ub Nishir.'
